DocAttribute.Name: PredefinedType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Qualifies the feature regarding its shape and configuration relative to the voided element.

DocWhereRule.Name: CorrectPredefinedType
DocWhereRule.Expression: NOT(EXISTS(PredefinedType)) OR (PredefinedType <> IfcVoidingFeatureTypeEnum.USERDEFINED) OR ((PredefinedType = IfcVoidingFeatureTypeEnum.USERDEFINED) AND EXISTS (SELF\IfcObject.ObjectType))
